title: Top 50 NFL Players Heading Into 2021
itunes:title: Top 50 NFL Players Heading Into 2021
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus and Gregg Rosenthal are joined by Cynthia Frelund to bring you all of the latest news around the NFL including a match between Aaron Rodgers and Brady and N'Keal Harry requesting a trade from the Patriots. Sam Monson from PFF joins the show to break down his top 50 list.
